f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有d可惜喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過係oslo要去睇三大石最快都要坐飛機去stavanger，再要搭車搭船來回搞幾個鐘都幾煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為真係好偏遠"}]}